{"tid":747023,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馮檢基：「港獨」使「一國兩制」前路艱難","createTime":"2018-07-18T05:15:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-18T10:35:52.000Z","uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7a53c6807930e20c5f749c19094789434e6639da","tid":747023,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T05:15:55.000Z","msg":"【大公報訊】記者高仁報道：保安局表明將考慮禁止「香港民族黨」的運作，近日抽身退出反對派政黨的馮檢基昨日痛斥反對派。對於反對派近年行為日益激進，出現掟磚，乃至提出「港獨」、「自決」等主張，他認為都是違反「一國兩制」。馮檢基明確表示，鼓吹「港獨」只會令「一國兩制」的前路愈加艱難。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.takungpao.com.hk/news/232109/2018/0718/189719.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.takungpao.com.hk%2Fnews%2F232109%2F2018%2F0718%2F189719.html&d=PfrH36aExH558%2Fh6JJQE0aWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=1d25cbed\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.takungpao.com.hk/news/232109/2018/0718/189719.html</a>"},{"pid":"5361e0e55a42bb56a93a772fc9531f66eac7ee8e","tid":747023,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T10:29:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5df009e8c4a84af4ba8d3be1241b92fc831cd5d9","tid":747023,"uid":47359,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T10:35:52.000Z","msg":"倒果為因<br />\n因為知道一國兩制係騙局先會搞港獨"}]}